576
00:33:30,213 --> 00:33:32,382
<i>Straighten your shoulders</i>

577
00:33:32,382 --> 00:33:35,852
<i>Erase all the hardships</i>

578
00:33:35,852 --> 00:33:37,120
<i>In the world</i>

579
